data.name: MigrateWorkbenchConnectionsButton.ToolTip
data.value: Migrates MySQL Server stored connections to the MySQL Workbench's connections file. This is only enabled if MySQL Workbench is installed and there are stored connections that can be merged with Workbench's connections.

data.name: UseColorfulIconsCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: When checked the Notifier icon displayed in the Windows System Tray is colored in a way to tell there is a change of status in one of the monitored services or MySQL Server instances. When unchecked the Notifier icon is always white-colored and to notice status changes the list of monitored services or MySQL Server instances must be inspected.
